        &nbsp;·&nbsp;
        <a href="https://tcgfast.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--color-text-muted); text-decoration: none;" class="hover:text-white">Docs</a>
        &nbsp;·&nbsp;
        <a href="https://github.com/TCG-Price-Lookup" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--color-text-muted); text-decoration: none;" class="hover:text-white">GitHub</a>
      </p>
      <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.75rem;">
